detailedDescription.articleBody:
Essam Kamal Tawfiq El-Hadary is an Egyptian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Ismaily.
Nicknamed the "High Dam", he has spent the largest portion of his club career with Al-Ahly, with whom he won eight Egyptian Premier League titles, four Egypt Cups, four Egyptian Super Cups, four CAF Champions League titles, three CAF Super Cups, one Arab Club Champions Cup, and two Arab Super Cups.
